    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled right off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself, you won't be disappointed!",
