    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the absolute definition of showroom quality. From the deep, mirror-like finish of the ceramic-coated exterior to the pristine, hand-stitched leather interior that still retains its new-car scent, every inch of this car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. There are zero blemishes, rock chips, or signs of interior wear. It performs exactly as it did the day it left the dealership, featuring crisp gear shifts and a responsive, powerful engine that has been serviced exclusively by master technicians. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a truly flawless example. The sale includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a comprehensive folder of documented service history.",
      "price": 48900.0,
