    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved vehicle, a benchmark of automotive excellence. Maintained in showroom condition, this specimen exhibits flawless paintwork and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Rigorously inspected and detail-perfect, it represents a premier acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. This vehicle is offered as a testament to superior care and engineering integrity.",
