    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, you\u2019ve found it! This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it\u2019s been garage-kept and meticulously cared for. It looks, smells, and drives like it\u2019s brand new. I\u2019m honestly sad to see it go, but I\u2019d love for it to find a great new home. Come check it out, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
