      "description": "Offering a collector-grade specimen featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM valvetrain. This unit boasts a comprehensive service history, including a proactive VANOS overhaul and reinforced subframe mounting points to ensure chassis rigidity under high lateral loads. The factory-spec limited-slip differential remains tight, and the suspension geometry is dialed to OEM precision. Finished in a flawless exterior with a preserved interior, this example represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Mechanically synchronized and aesthetically pristine, it is prepared for the most discerning driver.",
